<plot>"Democracy 4 Dummies" is a 'how to' documentary that shows curious cynics and aspiring politicians alike how to run for office, with little or no money. Mixing grassroots politics and Green Party candidates, the result is an election adventure stocked full of laughs and satirical commentary, which leaves even the most skeptical viewer thinking, "if these guys can do it, so can I!"</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?136152</url></doc>
